are decaying fast?

00:35:24.620 --> 00:35:26.220
High frequencies?

00:35:26.220 --> 00:35:30.750
If k is large, k
squared is very large

00:35:30.750 --> 00:35:34.690
and e to the minus k squared
t is decaying very quickly.

00:35:34.690 --> 00:35:39.840
So high-frequency
noise in this system,

00:35:39.840 --> 00:35:46.970
roughness, discontinuities
are going to get smoothed out,

00:35:46.970 --> 00:35:51.070
strongly, by moving
forward in time.

00:35:51.070 --> 00:35:52.750
Physically, what's
happening is, we

00:35:52.750 --> 00:36:00.020
